description: You'll wonder who's the prey and who's the predator when Adam Russo finds Club Inferno Exclusive Evan Matthews blindfolded and restrained in an abandoned warehouse. Matthews willingly takes every toy Russo shoves up his ass, eventually demanding more. Matthews astonishes Russo by opening his hole to display a brilliant rosebud before sucking in Russo's entire arm past the elbow!
title: Fist Trap, Scene #01
